high_descs: Turn left, walk forward to face the coffee maker.
Pick up the coffee cup sitting on the coffee maker.
Turn around to face the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, place the coffee cup on the right side of the top shelf. Close the refrigerator. Open the refrigerator, pick up the coffee cup. Close the refrigerator.
Turn to the left, turn to face the coffee maker.
Place the coffee cup on the coffee maker beside the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Pick up a coffee cup, place it in the refrigerator, move it to the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn left and walk up to the coffee maker
Pick up the white mug from the coffee maker
Move a few feet right to the fridge
Put the mug in the fridge then remove it
Turn left and walk back to the coffee maker
Put the mug in the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled mug in the coffee maker

high_descs: Take a step forward, then turn left and walk up to the coffee machine.
Pick up the mug that is in the coffee machine on the counter.
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn left and walk up to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and put the mug inside then close the fridge door, after a couple seconds open the fridge back up and remove the mug, then close the fridge door.
Turn left and walk towards the white table, then turn right and walk up to the coffee machine.
Put the chilled coffee mug into the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled coffee mug in the coffee machine.
